snippet.title: Trash Goblin - Announcement Trailer - "Goblin Etsy: the Videogame"
snippet.description:
A wholesome & cosy shopkeeping game where you uncover, repair and clean trinkets, then customise and upcycle them to sell to your colourful customers.

Spend your savings to upgrade your shop, buy new and better tools, even expand your business to exciting new districts across town!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2407830
Keep an eye on the upcoming Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/spiltmilkstudios/trash-goblin
Official website: https://www.trashgoblingame.com
Discord: https://discord.gg/spiltmilk
